{
  "stem": "2916.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That quite unexpectedly, mostly in the middle of the night, the Hungarian military police would come.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They would knock on the doors, and we had to open.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they would march in, two or three of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they would search the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They would have a warrant to search the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The search meant that they would open all the closets, spill out all the contents, stand up on top of the furniture, look behind curtains, poke even our couch and beds with their bayonets.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what were they searching for?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were searching for weapons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You can imagine that a small town person never even dreamt of seeing a weapon other than in the hands of the soldiers or the military police.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Weapons for-- concealed radio equipment, that we shouldn't contact secretly the allies about where the war is standing, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in the process of doing this, they would take things, whatever they saw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If a-- if a policeman would see a silver object, like there's a silver cup over there in the cabinet, then quickly he would put it in his pocket.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He would see a watch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In his other pocket, a bottle of perfume.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whatever quickly they would notice quickly, they would put in their pockets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they didn't even do it surreptitiously.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we could see it, and there was nothing we could do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We just watched them violate our privacy and take our possessions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had beautiful embroidered chairs, Goblin chairs, in the-- in the dining room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And sometimes in the winter, they would come with muddy boots.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they would not pull over a wooden chair to stand up if they want to reach a higher closet.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they would always stand on those chairs and mess them up.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
